        "zh-Hans": "清热药"
      },
      "pinyin": "Qīng Rè Yào",
      "categoryCode": "02",
      "description": {
        "en": "Clears heat and fire, treats heat patterns.",
        "zh-Hant": "清熱瀉火，治療熱證。"
      },
      "indications": {
        "en": "Fever, inflammation, heat patterns"
